{"tid":1551812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請投票］我設計左枝旗希望用嚟配合「願榮光歸香港」","createTime":"2019-09-08T07:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:48:31.000Z","uid":270500,"like":7,"dislike":157,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a46fb9c32f785852e4044fbc5aea29f0a3dab9fe","tid":1551812,"uid":270500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:39:51.000Z","msg":"歌曲：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=5add6632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5G4uca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5G4uca.png&h=a0f91c1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWidth:Height =1:2<br />\n<br />\n白：RGB 255 255 255<br />\n黃：RGB 255 255 0<br />\n藍：RGB 0     100  255<br />\n黑：RGB 0     0      0<br />\n<br />\n每色佔 Width 1/4<br />\n<br />\n設計概念：<br />\n1）「團結黃藍 分清黑白」；<br />\n呼應現行文宣<br />\n「黃藍是政見 黑白是良知」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）顏色依照左右翼順序，白黃藍黑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%A6%E6%B4%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%B3%E6%B4%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%258F%25B3%25E6%25B4%25BE&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=073bf106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%A6%E6%B4%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%B3%E6%B4%BE</a><br />\n<br />\n3）世界上國旗多以簡為主，所以沒加其他圖案 如 獅子山 剪影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=385c6e5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>正評=設計可行<br />\n負評=設計不可行</strong>"},{"pid":"9d12ac845380d7445edcce3f6320e2beb5fce09d","tid":1551812,"uid":76148,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"好撚柒"},{"pid":"f749949e3019e9f630df8aa9e0155df76ab63873","tid":1551812,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"黃黑藍白就一定要係主色架勒<br />\n但你呢支好似咩清朝定北洋旗"},{"pid":"3369b9ccf4db843e1c04b78328e8a98b038d89e8","tid":1551812,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"好似冇地方用黑色做國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a215ff33e95423e4a6575c28a91f3b00d38bccdd","tid":1551812,"uid":42340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"真係柒到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e147773373e6b3aa68905bada13ff3f19403a645","tid":1551812,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3369b9ccf4db843e1c04b78328e8a98b038d89e8","tid":1551812,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"好似冇地方用黑色做國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8c678bf41e2b7517b7114e0f9ba01771eca110","tid":1551812,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d12ac845380d7445edcce3f6320e2beb5fce09d","tid":1551812,"uid":76148,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"好撚柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />概念好好，但..."},{"pid":"2629e3e8ed08cc633c666c2a89ff74fe838d2b2c","tid":1551812,"uid":235152,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/109.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F109.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=372e409a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國旗用色以英國旗為基調配以暖黃突出國徽 紀念香港以英國文化之形響下成為集東西文化於一身之國度 國徽概念以洋紫荆之形浴火重生，以大鵬金翅鳥之形相重現 象徵香港歷中共浩刼而後自強獨立成國，必然有更美好前景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/110.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F110.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=7711a38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獅子山旗&mdash; 國旗由藍、白兩個平行相等的長方形及具象化的獅子山組成。正中的獅子象徵香港人不屈不撓的精神，中間的星代表港人獨立的意志和決心。藍色代表民主，自由；白色代表和平，公正。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/flags/94.jpg?v=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fflags%2F94.jpg%3Fv%3D1&h=f927caf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n木棉有英雄樹之稱，象徵香港雄視亞東；其花落不散，喻各地國民皆心繫母國；十八花蕊象徵十八區國民子嗣繁衍。金黃雲雷紋拱衛木棉，香港建國順天應人，承繼華夏。普魯士藍底色，象徵海洋，呼應英治。"},{"pid":"c98cedcddd68045b51e31ff859e4081cdee6e82a","tid":1551812,"uid":244149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e147773373e6b3aa68905bada13ff3f19403a645","tid":1551812,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3369b9ccf4db843e1c04b78328e8a98b038d89e8","tid":1551812,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:47:25.000Z","msg":"好似冇地方用黑色做國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"比利時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cdac3041cabed9f24b6cde3842397717fc9bbe","tid":1551812,"uid":126283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2629e3e8ed08cc633c666c2a89ff74fe838d2b2c","tid":1551812,"uid"